Package: usaspending.gov
Title: USASpending Federal Spending Data Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the USASpending.gov API v2.
    Search awards, agencies, spending by geography/time/category, recipients,
    federal accounts, and autocomplete. All functions return tibbles.
